Third-party data
----------------

The bundled word-frequency dictionaries
(app/src/main/assets/dictionaries/en.txt and tr.txt) are derived from:

  FrequencyWords by Hermit Dave
  https://github.com/hermitdave/FrequencyWords

  Generated from the OpenSubtitles 2018 corpus
  (https://opus.nlpl.eu/OpenSubtitles.php).

  Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
  (CC BY-SA 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

Modifications made for RimBoard: filtered to alphabetic words for each
language and truncated to the top 10,000 entries per language. Under the
CC BY-SA 4.0 terms, these dictionary files (and any derivative dictionary
files) remain licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0.
